Name: Hentai MatchUp
About the game: Hentai MatchUp is a concentration game, and what you need to do is to match all blocks. Gameplay Guide Victory Condition: Match all blocks. How to Play: Click on two blocks, and they will disappear if they have the same value. Function Keys Keyboard P: One key finish Keyboard S: Emergency avoidance (the background image turns white and you can continue to play) Keyboard N: Next level Game Features Pleasing Pictures Soothing Music
